videos.description: Ole Miss and Alabama are spotted getting into a scuffle just minutes before tipoff.
videos.headline: Ole Miss, Alabama get into scuffle pregame

videos.description: Avery Johnson Jr. tosses a pass off the backboard to Donta Hall who rises and slams it home.
videos.headline: Bama's Hall grabs pass off backboard and slams it home

videos.description: After a missed shot, Galin Smith gets the rebound and throws up a shoot to beat the buzzer at the end of the first half.
videos.headline: Alabama sinks floater to beat halftime buzzer
